## 5. Resource & Timeline Estimate
- 2 SDETs for automation scripting (4 weeks)
- 1 Performance Engineer for JMeter (2 weeks)
- 1 Security Engineer for ZAP (1 week)
- 1 Test Lead for coordination and reporting (project duration)
- Estimated execution: 6 weeks total (including parallelization and buffer)

