## 9. Risk Mitigation Table
| Risk ID | Description | Impact | Probability | Mitigation Action | Owner |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| R1 | Dynamic database connection drops during parallel test runs | High | Medium | Implement retry logic and DB connection pooling in PyTest | QA Team |
| R2 | SLA processing latency spikes under load | High | High | Early JMeter load simulation and SLA alerting | Perf Eng |
| R3 | UI element locator flakiness in Playwright | Medium | Medium | Use robust selectors and visual validation | SDET |
| R4 | Security scan false positives in ZAP | Medium | Low | Manual review of flagged issues | Sec Eng |
| R5 | Network throttling not reflecting real-world conditions | Medium | Medium | Calibrate tcconfig profiles with production logs | QA Team |

